quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,238,"Bobatela basambela, mpe sambela ya sima ya nzanga. Mpe botelema na limemia liboso ya Allah.",""
  2,239,"Mpe soki bobangi bosambela ya kotelema to likolo ya bampunda. Kasi soki bozui kimia bosambela Allah na ndenge atangisi bino maye boyebaki te.",""
  2,240,"Baye kati na bino liwa lizui bango mpe batiki basi, esengeli batikela bango malako. Mpe basala bango malamu mobu moko, kasi babengana bango na ndenge ya mabe te. Soki bango moko babimi mpe bakei, ezali mabe te likolo nabino na maye bango moko baponi na bolamu.Mpe Allah azali na bokasi atonda bwanya.",""
  2,241,"Mpe mpona basi bakufeli mabala esengeli kosalela bango limemia na lolenge ya malamu, ezali lotomo likolo ya babangi.",""
  2,242,"Na boye nde Allah azali kolimbola bino bilembo naye, mpo ete bososola.",""
  2,243,"Ozali komona te baye babimaki na bandako na bango bazalaki bankoto mpe bango babangi liwa? Mpe Allah alobi na bango: bokufa. Sima asekwisi bango. Ya s么l贸, Allah aleki kosalela bato bolamu, mpe kasi bato ebele bazali kotondo ye te.",""
  2,244,"Mpe bobunda na nzela ya Allah, mpe boyeba ete ya s么l贸 Allah azali moyoki moyebi ya manso.",""
  2,245,"Oyo azali kosalela Allah mosala malamu, akobakisela ye mbala ebele, mpe Allah akangaka bozui mpe afungolaka. Mpe epai naye nde bokozongisama.",""
